    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"395\" data-end=\"446\">Nothing Left to Lose (Passive; Rage + Bloodied)</strong><br data-start=\"446\" data-end=\"449\" />When you are cornered, you become terrifying.</p><p data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"613\">While you are <strong data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"520\">raging</strong> and <strong data-start=\"525\" data-end=\"537\">bloodied</strong> (at or below half your hit point maximum), you gain the following benefits:</p><ul data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"806\"><li data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"719\"><p data-start=\"617\" data-end=\"719\">You have <strong data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"640\">resistance</strong> to <strong data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"683\">bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing</strong> damage from <strong data-start=\"696\" data-end=\"718\">nonmagical attacks</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"720\" data-end=\"806\"><p data-start=\"722\" data-end=\"806\"><strong data-start=\"722\" data-end=\"739\">Once per turn</strong>, when you hit a creature, you may deal <strong data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"805\">+1d8 additional damage</strong>.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"808\" data-end=\"882\"><strong data-start=\"808\" data-end=\"846\">When this feature first activates:</strong> You gain <strong data-start=\"856\" data-end=\"881\">1 level of exhaustion</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"958\">This feature ends if your <strong data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"923\">Rage ends</strong> or you are <strong data-start=\"935\" data-end=\"957\">no longer bloodied</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"960\" data-end=\"963\" /><p data-start=\"965\" data-end=\"1027\"><br /><code data-start=\"986\" data-end=\"1027\">[GAROU_FEATURE] id=nothing-left-to-lose</code></p>",
